# ACE-Step API Documentation
## For Shoosty Studio / Dadbot Music Pipeline

**Last Updated:** June 9, 2026  
**Working Image:** `shoosty1/ace-step:v28`  
**Endpoint:** `pd2iixy9kh509f`

---

## Quick Reference

| Parameter | Type | Required | Limit |
|-----------|------|----------|-------|
| `caption` | string | yes | 512 characters max |
| `lyrics` | string | no | ~4000 tokens shared with audio |
| `duration` | integer | no | 10–600 seconds (default: 30) |
| `lora_url` | string | no | URL to .safetensors file |

---

## API Endpoint

```
POST https://api.runpod.ai/v2/pd2iixy9kh509f/run
```

**Headers:**
```
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_RUNPOD_API_KEY
Content-Type: application/json
```

---

## Request Payload

### Instrumental (no vocals)
```json
{
  "input": {
    "caption": "progressive synth, analog synthesizers, gated drums, bright catchy hook, spatial reverb, 120bpm",
    "lyrics": "[Instrumental]",
    "duration": 180
  }
}
```

### With Vocals
```json
{
  "input": {
    "caption": "progressive synth, analog synthesizers, gated drums, retrofuture, warm bass, 120bpm",
    "lyrics": "[Verse 1]\nYour lyrics here\n\n[Chorus]\nYour chorus here\n\n[Bridge]\nYour bridge here",
    "duration": 180
  }
}
```

### With LoRA (style fine-tuning)
```json
{
  "input": {
    "caption": "progressive synth, analog synthesizers, gated drums",
    "lyrics": "[Verse 1]\nYour lyrics here",
    "duration": 180,
    "lora_url": "https://your-storage.com/your-lora.safetensors"
  }
}
```

