## Lyrics Format

ACE-Step supports structured lyrics with section tags. Use these markers:

```
[Verse 1]
Line one of verse
Line two of verse

[Chorus]
Your catchy hook
Repeated hook line

[Verse 2]
Second verse content

[Bridge]
The bridge section

[Outro]
Final lines
Fade out
```

**Special tags:**
- `[Instrumental]` — no vocals, pure music
- `[Instrumental break]` — instrumental section within a vocal song
- `[Intro]` — opening section
- `[Outro]` — closing section
- `[Pre-chorus]` — build before chorus

