## Duration Guide

| Song Type | Duration |
|-----------|----------|
| Short clip / test | 10–30s |
| Single verse | 45–60s |
| Full pop song | 180–240s |
| Epic / long form | 300–600s |

**Note:** Longer songs with heavy lyrics may hit context limits. For songs over 3 minutes, use `[Instrumental]` breaks to give the model breathing room.

