## Error Handling

The handler returns errors in the response rather than failing silently:

```json
{
  "output": {
    "error": "Models not found at /runpod-volume/...",
    "traceback": "full Python traceback here"
  }
}
```

Always check for `output.error` before trying to decode `output.audio_b64`.

