## Known Limitations

- Caption hard limit: 512 characters
- Max duration: 600 seconds (10 minutes)
- With heavy lyrics, practical max ~3–4 minutes before context exhaustion
- Base model vocals sound synthetic — use LoRA for character voice
- First cold start after idle: ~25 extra seconds
- Official ACE-Step v0.1.8 image requires CUDA 12.8 — RunPod currently at 12.4, use `shoosty1/ace-step:v28` instead

