## The Lesson That Took 4 Days

RunPod serverless mounts network volumes at `/runpod-volume` — **NOT** `/workspace`.

The models were always there. Nobody looked in the right place.

```python
# WRONG - caused 27 failed versions
checkpoint = "/workspace/models/..."

# RIGHT - v28, works
checkpoint = "/runpod-volume/models/..."
```

